section_label: Three images showing various views of the property
raw_md_fragment:
[IMAGE]
Three images showing various views of the property:
1. Side view of the building showing a narrow alleyway and adjacent properties.
1. Rear view showing a parking area with several cars.
1. Close-up of the building's electrical meters mounted on the exterior wall.
[/IMAGE]

[IMAGE]
Image showing a stairwell with brick walls and mailboxes on the right side. The stairwell has a carpeted floor and metal railings.
[/IMAGE]

[IMAGE]
Image of a hallway with a wooden door and a painting on the wall. The floor is carpeted, and there is a metal railing on the stairs.
[/IMAGE]

[IMAGE]
Image of a brick building exterior with a red awning over the entrance. The building has multiple windows with air conditioning units.
[/IMAGE]
